Electron based
-No top bar, frameless window
-function as a web browser
    -Browser tab functionality
    -Each tab is added as a tiled window within the application, the same way a twm window is tiled
using shortcuts that do not interfere with the browser's own shortcuts or OS shortcuts
    -tabs can be resized, moved, created and closed using keyboard shortcuts
no URL bar or similar, the user can only navigate to a URL by opening a new tab and entering the URL in the address bar of that tab
